:<font size="15">שׁלישׁי</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
שׁלישׁי / shelîyshîy / shel-ee-shee'

===Etymology===
Ordinal from  שׁלושׁ  shâlôsh   {{HH|7969}}; 

===Cardinal number===
'''שׁלישׁי'''

# [[third]]; feminine a third (part); by extension a third (day, year or time); specifically a third story cell): - third (part, rank, time), [[three]] (years old).

